Isn't This Neat? Spectrum's The Little Mermaid Disney Collection Features Treasures Untold

By Lucy Kenny
Updated on June 10, 2018 at 8:40 AM

If you've ever speculated about how many wonders one cavern can really hold, wait until you see Spectrum's collaboration with Disney's The Little Mermaid. We're convinced the company that brought us beauty's answer to Mean Girl's iconic Burn Book is on a mission to give Disney fans heart palpitations, because its newest collection is truly that good. From Ursula vanity cases to mermaid makeup brushes, the collection is filled with gadgets and gizmos aplenty that will make you feel part of Ariel's world with one flick of a foundation brush. Unfortunately, there is one catch — the collaboration is only available in the UK and Ireland, so poor, unfortunate souls in the US need to start chatting up friends across the pond ASAP!
